Cutoff electrostatics, part of ANU-Chem

This program is controlled by the Eclipse Public Licence v1.0 
http://www.eclipse.org/legal/epl-v10.html

Introduction
------------

This example code calculates electrostatic potential energy for a system of
charged particles with periodic boundary conditions, using a simple cutoff.

Compile dependencies:
------------------------
* X10 version 2.5 (optionally with x10rt=mpi)
* XLA library (cd ~/anuchem-code/x10x.lib/xla && ant)
* anu-chem library (cd ~/anuchem-code/anuchem && ant)


